com.camerontec.catalys.server.compliance

Interface IFilterStateController

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractFilterStateController, ConcurrentOrderFilterStateController, ExposureFilterStateController, FilterStateControllerContainer, GrossExposureFilterStateController, GrossTradeExposureFilterStateController, NetExposureFilterStateController, NetTradeExposureFilterStateController, TradeExposureFilterStateController

    public interface IFilterStateController
    IFilterStateController is an interface describing a filter state controller. The responsibility of a filter state controller is to update any state that is required to managed in order for particular filters to operate. A compliance filter may be associated with a filter state controiler. Multiple filters may use the same filter state controller.
    Author:
    Tom Vasak
